---
import Button from '@/components/shared/Button.astro';
import SectionHeader from '@/components/shared/SectionHeader.astro';
import classes from '@/data/styles.json';
import Card from '@/components/Card.astro';
---

<section class="bg-secondary py-24" id="about">
  <div class={classes.container}>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:flex-row">
      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/3">
        <SectionHeader
          preHeading="Customer Obsession"
          heading={['Building for', ' real people.']}
        />
        <p class={classes.primaryText}>
          It’s about the person on the other side of the screen, not just the browser. To me, code
          is just a tool to make someone’s day a little easier. I sweat the technical details—like
          speed and accessibility—so the user gets a smooth, frustration-free experience every time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:w-2/3">
        <Card
          icon="accessibility_new"
          title="Inclusive UI & Design"
          description="Bridging creative vision and engineering, I translate Figma designs into pixel-perfect interfaces strictly adhering to WCAG 2.1/AODA. From semantic HTML to micro-interactions, I ensure a seamless, inclusive experience for every user on any device."
        />
        <Card
          offset
          icon="bolt"
          title="Performance"
          description="I optimize for the user's time by targeting Core Web Vitals to achieve high Lighthouse scores. By prioritizing the Critical Rendering Path and utilizing strategies like intelligent code-splitting and asset optimization, I engineer zero-latency experiences that build user trust."
        />
        <Card
          icon="integration_instructions"
          title="Scalable Architecture"
          description="Features change, but the system must hold. I leverage TypeScript and modular, component-driven patterns to build robust architectures. By prioritizing type safety and preventing technical debt upfront, I create environments where teams can ship rapidly without fear of breaking production."
        />
        <Card
          offset
          icon="verified"
          title="Engineering Excellence"
          description="I elevate team velocity by combining mentorship with modern automation. Through rigorous code reviews, AI-enhanced workflows (GitHub Copilot), and robust CI/CD pipelines, I remove friction from the development cycle—ensuring we deliver stable, high-value software faster than ever."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
